{% comment %}
  Shipping Policy Page
{% endcomment %}

<div class="pt-32 pb-24 min-h-screen bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <h1 class="font-serif-display text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-2 text-gray-900">{{ page.title }}</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-12">Last updated: {{ 'now' | date: '%B %Y' }}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-700">
      
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Shipping Methods</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Standard Shipping</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">5-7 business days • FREE on orders over $150</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Delivery time is estimated and not guaranteed. International orders may take longer.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">Express Shipping</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">1-2 business days • $24.99</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Expedited shipping for urgent orders.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900">International Shipping</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">10-15 business days • Calculated at checkout</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">We ship to most countries worldwide. Customs and duties may apply.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Order Processing</h2>
        <p>Orders are processed within 1-2 business days during business hours (Monday-Friday, 9am-6pm CET). Orders placed during weekends or holidays will be processed the next business day.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Tracking Your Order</h2>
        <p>Once your order ships, you'll receive an email with a tracking number. You can track your package using this number on the carrier's website.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Shipping Delays</h2>
        <p>While we strive for on-time delivery, delays can occur due to weather, customs, or carrier issues. We are not liable for delays caused by third-party carriers.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif-display text-2xl text-gray-900 mb-4">Lost or Damaged Packages</h2>
        <p>If your package arrives damaged or doesn't arrive within the estimated timeframe, please contact us immediately with photos and tracking information. We will file a claim with the carrier or resend your order.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="bg-pink-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-pink-200 mt-12">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Have questions about shipping?</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@lahime.com" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">contact@lahime.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .font-serif-display { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; }
</style>
